Consumed gas: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">2</code></p>
<h2 id="security-considerations">
<a href="#security-considerations" class="anchor-link"></a> Security Considerations
</h2>
<p>The value of the base fee is not sensitive and is publicly accessible in the block header. There are no known security implications with this opcode.</p>
